# Blueprint UI Patterns

## Color System (Always Use CSS Variables)

```css
:root {
  /* Primary Blues */
  --color-bg-primary: #0047AB;      /* Cobalt blue - main background */
  --color-bg-deep: #001F54;         /* Navy - shadows */
  --color-bg-surface: #0052CC;      /* Lighter blue - panels */
  
  /* Grid & Lines */
  --color-grid: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  --color-grid-major: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  --color-line-annotation: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  
  /* Text */
  --color-text-primary: #FFFFFF;
  --color-text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  --color-text-annotation: #00D4FF;
  
  /* Accents */
  --color-accent-glow: #00D4FF;
}
```

