## Component Patterns

### Blueprint Annotations
```tsx
<div className="annotation">
  <span className="annotation-title">TOOL NAME</span>
  <p className="annotation-desc">Description here</p>
</div>
```

Annotation styling:
- Font: monospace
- Color: `var(--color-text-annotation)`
- Left border: 2px solid with annotation line color
- Uppercase title with letter-spacing

